you can see that it's 600 kb.

00:05:58.040 --> 00:06:00.260
What do we can compress
it even more in

00:06:00.260 --> 00:06:02.765
order to increase
our page load speed.

00:06:02.765 --> 00:06:05.105
But how there are
different ways you can use

00:06:05.105 --> 00:06:09.125
Adobe Photoshop and you can
use the Save for Web option.

