There we go. This
is our new image,

00:06:52.430 --> 00:06:54.140
although we compress it,

00:06:54.140 --> 00:06:56.255
it still has a high-quality.

00:06:56.255 --> 00:06:58.880
So you need to always
go ahead and compress

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:02.269
your images before importing
them into Webflow.

