We have different settings.

00:07:25.070 --> 00:07:26.270
If you remember, we have

00:07:26.270 --> 00:07:29.150
the alt texts and here
we have the load option.

00:07:29.150 --> 00:07:33.800
Since 2020, all images by
default are set to lazy load.

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:35.135
But what does it mean?

00:07:35.135 --> 00:07:36.905
Let me remove this
image elements.

00:07:36.905 --> 00:07:38.765
I'm going to select
this hero image.

00:07:38.765 --> 00:07:41.210
And if I click on
the Settings icon,

00:07:41.210 --> 00:07:43.445
